      "body" : "Actually, there are rules: &quot;The prefix of a unique package name is always written in all-lowercase ASCII letters&quot; (<a href=\"http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/codeconventions-135099.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">oracle.com/technetwork/java/codeconventions-135099.html</a>)"
    } ],
