    "body" : "<p>Concatenation of words in the package name is something most developers don't do. </p>\n\n<p>You can use something like. </p>\n\n<p><code>com.stackoverflow.mypackage</code></p>\n\n<p>Refer <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/specs/jls/se8/html/jls-6.html#jls-6.1\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">JLS Name Declaration</a></p>\n"
